'''Aktepe Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Ankara]], [[Turkey]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home of [[Ankaraspor]]. The stadium holds 5,000 people and was built in 1999.

