'''Belmopan Bandits Sports Club''' is a [[Belize]]an [[Association football|football]] team which currently competes in the [[Premier League of Belize]].<ref>{{cite news|title= Premier League of Belize kicks off this weekend |url=http://amandala.com.bz/news/premier-league-of-belize-kicks-off-this-weekend/|accessdate=4 February 2012|newspaper=Amandala Online|date=3 February 2012}}</ref>

The team is based in the capital city of [[Belize]], [[Belmopan]]. The team currently plays its home games at [[Isidoro Beaton Stadium]] in [[Belmopan]]. The stadium can hold 2,500 spectators.

Belmopan have occasionally held home games in international competitions at [[FFB Stadium]] in [[Belmopan]], which has a capacity of 5,000 spectators.

